{{zh-hanzi|[[既]][[生]][[瑜]]，[[何]][[生]][[亮]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: jì shēng yú, hé shēng liàng
===Etymology===
Literally: [[w:Zhou Yu|Zhou Yu]] has already been born, so why was [[w:Zhuge Liang|Zhuge Liang]] ever born?
*[[w:Zhou Yu|Zhou Yu]] was young and ambitious, but was always being upstaged by [[w:Zhuge Liang|Zhuge Liang]], who was more talented.
===Idiom===
# used to lament the fact that there is someone better than you who is outshining you at every turn; to [[bemoan]] a new contender
#: ''[[微软]][[掐架]][[索尼]] [[游戏机]]'''既生瑜何生亮''''' [http://72.14.203.104/search?q=cache:l5niAMQf9MkJ:www.hebei.com.cn/node2/node17/node1077/userobject1ai369164.html+%22%E6%97%A2%E7%94%9F%E7%91%9C%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%95%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%AE%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=12]
#: ''[[微軟]][[掐架]][[索尼]] [[遊戲機]]'''既生瑜何生亮'''''
#: ''[[Microsoft]] dukes it out with [[Sony]]; [[w:Video game console|Video game console]] makers '''bemoan the new contender'''''
